<item>
            <title>[LU-7661] MGS_SET_INFO handler is too permissive</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-7661</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The handler for &lt;tt&gt;MGS_SET_INFO&lt;/tt&gt; is needed only for the hack where setting the default striping on the root directory sets the default striping of the FS. It only needs to handle &apos;&lt;tt&gt;&amp;#42;.lov.stripe{count,size,offset}=&amp;#42;&lt;/tt&gt;&apos;. So we should only allow those params to be set.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
